window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It was only meant to be a one-night thing.</b> </p> <p>I work hard and party harder. Women come and go and I’m happy to show then the door when their time is up. </p> <p>The moment my eyes land on her I’m captivated. </p> <p>There’s only one place she’s spending this New Year's Eve, in my bed. </p> <p>But what if she’s not like all the others? What if one night isn’t enough? </p> <p>I’m falling for a woman, a stranger who’s too young for me but I can’t resist a taste. </p> <p><i>Falling for Daniel is a hot and steamy older man younger woman standalone novella from her Falling series world.</i></p>"; 
